data.description: Great location!  Cul-de-sac.  Near park, walking trail, restaurants and shopping. Walking distance to Overland Trail Middle School. Lower level walks out to a large patio. Enjoy the mornings surrounded by flowering Morning Glories and a water feature. Mature trees provide shade and privacy. Custom wood trim and fresh interior paint. Fenced back yard with a 8 X 10 shed. Extra wide driveway and a heated garage!
